Package modules.report

This package contains classes and interfaces needed for the Reprint Reporting module including report parameter page, the socket component for report request submital, and the report viewer.

See:
          Description

Interface Summary
ReportDao DAO Interface for accessing reporting configuration data.
 

Class Summary
ReportConstants Class containing constants regarding the Reprint reporting module.
ReportDetailListCellRenderer Cell renderer for the report detail list component.
ReportDetailListModelImpl Launch Pad's implementation of AbstractListModel for the report detail list component.
ReportFactory A factory for creating Print/Reprint Report Administration related objects.
ReportHeaderListCellRenderer Cell renderer for the report header list component.
ReportHeaderListModelImpl Launch Pad's implementation of AbstractListModel for the report header list component.
ReportIbatisDaoImpl This is the iBatis implementation of ReportDao interface for Print/Reprint Report Administration module.
ReportRequestFrame Window for allowing the user to setup and submit requests for various reports.
ReportRequestWorker A worker class for sending a report request to the UNIX server and displaying the results of the report request via the ReportViewer.
ReportTextFinderFrame Displays the results of a report's find operation and allows the user to view the results on a page by page basis.
ReportViewer A report viewer for displaying the results of a report request.
 

Exception Summary
ReportWorkerException Exception class for identifying situations where a report worker fails during the sending of the request to the UNIX server.
 

Package modules.report Description

This package contains classes and interfaces needed for the Reprint Reporting module including report parameter page, the socket component for report request submital, and the report viewer.
